Welcome to Murphy's Irish Pub Mandurah, Western Australia Our Story Established in 2008, Murphy's Irish Pub has been locally owned & operated ever since. Located in the heart of Mandurah Foreshore overlooking Mandjar Bay, we provide great entertainment most nights of the week free for all patrons including free trivia on Monday’s, Karaoke Wednesday, live soloists on Thursdays (excl winter), live bands Fridays & Saturdays before winding down with our Sunday sessions. We have a large selection of beer & cider on tap and also serve a great selection of wines, spirits, cocktails & coffees. Our delicious menu is far from the norm “pub food”. Our food is a favourite for locals and tourists for our great quality, big serves & delicious selection. If it’s live sport you’re after, then come and watch all the coverage on one of our 6 plasma screens or two huge cinema screens. We show a great variety of local & international sports so you’ll be sure to find the sporting match you’re after at Murphy’s. Showing matches on Optus Sports, STAN, HD Foxtel & Digital-TV. Check out our gallery Dining at Murphy's Chef's cooking 7 days a week! 11am 'til late Bookings recommended. Click the navigation bars at the top to make your reservation. View Our Menu Enjoy our menu for lunch & dinner, and all day on weekends. Most days we have a snack menu midweek between lunch & dinner (depending on chef availability) See our chalkboard inside for more daily chef specials For reservations you can now book online. For tables larger than 8, please contact the venue on (08) 9535 2666. Lunch & Dinner Menu Upcoming Events AFL Grand Final & All Blacks v Wallabies Sat, 27 Sept Mandurah Learn more Country Festival - Official After-Party venue! Sat, 25 Oct Mandurah Learn more Current Dining Specials & Deals Cold Beers on Tap We serve a large selection of products on tap including all the best Irish brands like Guinness, Kilkenny & Magners Cider. Plus 9 other great beers on tap including Hahn SuperDry full-strength & mid-strength, Heineken, Little Creatures, Swan Draught & a few more. We serve a great range of wines, spirits & cocktails too. ​Join us for Happy Hour 5pm-6pm Monday to Friday.
